text: Seagoville ( ) is a city in Dallas County, Texas, United States, and a suburb of Dallas. A small portion of Seagoville goes into Kaufman County. The population was 18,446 at the 2020 census. The city is located along U.S. Highway 175. It is from downtown Mesquite. ==References== Category:Cities in Dallas County, Texas
title: Seagoville, Texas
